{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And yet...as clear as those moments are in my life...for years there were questions.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I would have bad seasons with God or more specifically...without Him.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I would run into sin and addiction and problems that are common to all teenage and college age boys.\
